          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Helicopter Fuel System Safety Act</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits a person from operating a newly manufactured helicopter in U.S. airspace unless the Federal Aviation Administration certifies that the helicopter's design complies with certain crash resistant fuel system requirements.</p>]]></text>
